				<td colspan="2"><span>While twisting 4 songs, Zek, Muse, Psalm of Veeshan and Marr... sometimes you'll have 1 song fade off, especially if you are chatting while twisting... but question that came to my mind...
<br />

<br />
If you sing Call of the Muse... it takes hold.. caster starts to cast his nuke... and sure, the DD focus takes effects.
<br />

<br />
But, if you were singing call of the muse, caster starts to cast his nuke, Call of the Muse wears off before his nuke is finished casting... does the DD focus still take effect?
<br />

<br />
Or can he start casting, then Call of the Muse takes hold just before he finishes casting his nuke, the DD focus now takes effect?
<br />

<br />
*ponders*
<br />

<br />
Enadil Elvensinger</span></td>
