				<td colspan="2"><span>I did some testing a while back as I had some questions regarding when the damage was assigned as well, especially for dots.  I posted my results on the Concert Hall here:
<br />

<br />
http://pub147.ezboard.com/ftheconcerthallcenterstage.showMessage?topicID=399.topic
<br />

<br />
In short, as long as the CotM buff symbol is up as the spell or dot tick lands, the added damage is applied.  It doesn't matter if they started casting or not, it just has to be up when the spell hits the mob.</span></td>
